Elna Mansdotter

Anna Hansdotter was born on the 1st of June, 1800 to Elna Mansdotter and Hans Olsson in Warby, Bara parish, Malmöhus county (1A). Her father passed away when she was 13 years old and her mother remarried the following year to Jacob Jonsson in 1814 (1C). Three years later, the family moved to No. 5 1/2 Lyngby in Lyngby parish (1D) although it seems that Anna left home shortly after as she doesn’t show up in the household examination record for Elna and Jacob (1E).
